  "text": "For the development of this assistance system, the project pursues an approach in which reflexive, responsive, and deliberative dimensions have been integrated in various modules. [CITATION_1] Acoustic information means synthetic language, spatial sonification with artificial tones, spatial sonification with representative tones, use of Spearcons, Acusticons, and so on.",
