      "span_text": "For the development of this assistance system, the project pursues an approach in which reflexive, responsive, and deliberative dimensions have been integrated in various modules. Acoustic information means synthetic language, spatial sonification with artificial tones, spatial sonification with representative tones, use of Spearcons, Acusticons, and so on."
